<div><head>《五經大義》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.2">鄭注喪服云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.3">凡妻從夫降一等。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.4">夫合三月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.5">則妻宜無服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.6">而猶三月者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.7">古者大夫不外娶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.8">其妻則本國之女也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.9">雖後而出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.10">婦人歸宗往來，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.11">故從人服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.12">長子有服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.13">謂末去者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.14">逵謂鄭元注喪服不通，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.15">何者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.16">婦人義無二尊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.17">故出嫁則降父而服夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.18">何至為人去國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.19">乃兼服二君乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.20">若果宜兩服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.21">夫經紀應允，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.22">將謂大夫於君之母妻本有𧞓斬之殊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.23">乃仕焉而已，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.24">則俱在三月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.25">蓋其義也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-1a.26">杜佑《通典》卷九十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.2">大功殤服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.3">七月九月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.4">范甯與逵書問馬、鄭二義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.5">逵答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.6">夫易者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.7">當使用日則廢月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.8">可得言易耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.9">鄭以哭日准平生之月而謂之易，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.10">且無服之殤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.11">非唯周親七歲以下也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.12">他親長中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.13">降而不服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.14">故傳曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.15">不滿八歲已下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.16">皆為無服之殤也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.17">如馬義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.18">則以文悉關諸服降之殤若；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.19">如鄭義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.20">諸降之殤當作何哭耶？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.21">若復哭其生月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.22">則緦麻之長殤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.23">決不可二百餘日哭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.24">鄭必推之於不哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.25">則小功之親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.26">以老學之年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.27">成童而夭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.28">無哭泣之位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.29">恐非有情者之所允也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-2a.30">《通典》卷九十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-3a.2">披榛而遊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-3a.3">遇穴而處，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-3a.4">男無定居，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-3a.5">女無常處。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1195_CHANT_001-3a.6">虞世南《北堂書鈔‧地部》引戴逵《雜義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
